Single quantitative variable
========================================================
transition:none

```{r}
df_onequant <- birthwt %>%
    dplyr::select(birth_weight = bwt) %>%
    tbl_df()

df_onequant
```

***

Histogram

```{r}
ggplot(df_onequant, aes(x = birth_weight)) +
    geom_histogram(color = "black", fill = "white") +
    xlab("Birth Weight (gm)")
```


Single quantitative variable
