***

Tabular summaries

* Five-number summary (or use other quantiles)

```{r, results = 'asis'}
df_onequant_table <- df_onequant$birth_weight %>%
    quantile() %>%
    as.data.frame()

colnames(df_onequant_table) <- c("Birth Weight (gm)")

df_onequant_table <- df_onequant_table %>%
    xtable() %>%
    print(type = "html", comment = FALSE)
```

